    + Favor additionalOption entries in maven-javadoc-plugin
    + Fix typo in Javadoc
    + Improve AssertFactory Javadoc
    + Add Throwable stack trace to ShouldHaveCauseExactlyInstance
    + Fix typo
    + Add Throwable stack trace to ShouldHaveCauseInstance
